================================================================================
DEPENDENCIES NOTICE
================================================================================

This software requires the following external services/software:

- Zotero (https://www.zotero.org/) - for reference management
- OpenAI API (optional) - for GPT model access
- Ollama (optional) - for local LLM deployment

================================================================================
DATA PRIVACY AND USAGE NOTICE
================================================================================

PyZoBot offers two operational modes:

1. Cloud-based: Uses OpenAI's API services. Data is processed according to 
   OpenAI's data usage policies.

2. Local/Private: Uses Ollama with open-source models. All data processing 
   occurs locally on your machine.

Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with their institutional data 
handling policies when processing research documents.

